sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Sender as "Sender Device (iPad or PC)"
    participant Receiver as "Receiver Device (PC or iPad)"
    participant Edge as "Edge Function API"
    participant DB as "Postgres transfer_sessions"
    participant ST as "Storage private bucket"
    participant RT as "Realtime channel transfer:sessionId"
    participant GC as "Cleanup worker"

    Note over Sender,Receiver: Clients use publishable key + user JWT only

    Sender->>Edge: create_transfer(receiverId fileName mime bytes sha256)
    Edge->>DB: insert session status=created sender_id receiver_id
    Edge-->>Sender: sessionId

    Sender->>Edge: request_upload_url(sessionId)
    Edge->>ST: create signed upload URL (short TTL)
    Edge-->>Sender: signed upload URL
    Sender->>ST: upload file object transfers/sessionId/file

    Sender->>Edge: finalize_upload(sessionId bytes sha256)
    Edge->>DB: update status=ready expected_bytes expected_sha256
    Edge->>RT: broadcast FILE_READY to receiver channel

    Receiver->>Edge: request_download_url(sessionId)
    Edge->>DB: verify receiver owns session and status=ready
    Edge->>ST: create signed download URL (short TTL)
    Edge-->>Receiver: signed download URL
    Receiver->>ST: download full object
    Receiver->>Edge: confirm_receipt(sessionId bytes sha256)

    Edge->>DB: verify bytes and sha256 match expected
    alt receipt valid
        Edge->>DB: update status=delivered delivered_at=now
        Edge->>GC: enqueue delete_object(sessionId)
        GC->>ST: delete transfers/sessionId/file
        alt delete success
            GC->>DB: update status=cleaned cleaned_at=now
            Edge->>RT: broadcast TRANSFER_COMPLETE_CLEANED
        else delete failed
            GC->>DB: update status=cleanup_failed retry_count+1
            GC->>GC: retry with backoff (idempotent)
        end
    else receipt invalid
        Edge->>DB: update status=receipt_mismatch
        Edge->>RT: broadcast RECEIPT_MISMATCH
    end

    Note over Edge,GC: Scheduled TTL cleanup removes stale unconfirmed objects
